you're human trash!

00:31:05.570 --> 00:31:07.802 position:24% line:89% align:start
The king of trash!

00:31:13.038 --> 00:31:16.271 position:19% line:83% align:start
Trash? What does that
old witch know anyway?

00:31:32.275 --> 00:31:32.209 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes?

00:31:33.875 --> 00:31:35.809 position:5% line:89% align:start
I want to get rid of some trash.

00:31:41.677 --> 00:31:43.278 position:19% line:89% align:start
I don't think I'd fit.

00:31:45.312 --> 00:31:49.313 position:16% line:83% align:start
Yeah, that's what I am,
human trash!

00:31:51.847 --> 00:31:55.047 position:21% line:83% align:start
Who cares if you die
in the gutter?

00:31:57.081 --> 00:31:59.949 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're dead all the same.

00:32:22.521 --> 00:32:24.054 position:35% line:89% align:start
You okay?

00:32:25.554 --> 00:32:27.122 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hang in there, Gramps.

00:32:30.789 --> 00:32:32.989 position:7% line:83% align:start
-May I make one last request?
-What?

00:32:35.491 --> 00:32:36.990 position:16% line:89% align:start
Give me a drink of that.

00:32:43.459 --> 00:32:45.359 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Spanish]

00:33:22.468 --> 00:33:24.934 position:35% line:89% align:start
[Spanish]

00:33:28.835 --> 00:33:30.402 position:19% line:83% align:start
