into slavery!

00:33:32.870 --> 00:33:34.703 position:27% line:89% align:start
Somebody, help!

00:33:50.107 --> 00:33:53.674 position:7% line:83% align:start
I always wanted to die drunk,
in a nice old house.

00:33:53.674 --> 00:33:56.942 position:19% line:89% align:start
Now I'm halfway there.

00:33:56.942 --> 00:33:58.409 position:10% line:89% align:start
Fate works in strange ways.

00:34:00.009 --> 00:34:01.144 position:16% line:89% align:start
I've lived a long time,

00:34:03.611 --> 00:34:05.411 position:21% line:83% align:start
but I'm just trash,
as worthless dead as alive.

00:34:06.844 --> 00:34:07.944 position:19% line:89% align:start
Don't talk like that!

00:34:10.246 --> 00:34:13.246 position:16% line:83% align:start
You remind me of myself
when I was younger.

00:34:14.614 --> 00:34:16.013 position:21% line:89% align:start
