if it's known who I am.

00:34:30.917 --> 00:34:33.217 position:21% line:83% align:start
Okay. I understand.
No one will ever know.

00:34:48.421 --> 00:34:51.721 position:10% line:83% align:start
Take care of yourself, okay?
May I make a last...?

00:34:52.556 --> 00:34:53.722 position:38% line:89% align:start
Request?

00:34:59.723 --> 00:35:01.991 position:24% line:89% align:start
And now, goodbye.

00:35:17.660 --> 00:35:18.262 position:35% line:89% align:start
That's it!

00:35:22.195 --> 00:35:23.229 position:27% line:89% align:start
Thanks, Gramps!

00:35:29.997 --> 00:35:31.964 position:33% line:83% align:start
