00:36:18.041 --> 00:36:18.742 position:13% line:89% align:start
My father was a policeman!

00:36:19.842 --> 00:36:20.942 position:24% line:89% align:start
Father, policeman?

00:36:24.443 --> 00:36:28.977 position:24% line:83% align:start
Except I'm the one
he's going to be arresting.

00:36:44.147 --> 00:36:44.948 position:38% line:89% align:start
Hold it.

00:36:48.749 --> 00:36:50.349 position:21% line:89% align:start
Hi! How've you been?

00:36:53.716 --> 00:36:54.683 position:19% line:89% align:start
