00:36:55.651 --> 00:36:57.717 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hey, wake up!

00:36:57.717 --> 00:36:58.784 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come on!

00:37:02.586 --> 00:37:04.119 position:30% line:89% align:start
No! Not that!

00:37:05.885 --> 00:37:07.886 position:19% line:89% align:start
Time to die, old man!

00:37:07.886 --> 00:37:10.020 position:13% line:89% align:start
Kiyo's coming? I'm there!

00:37:11.987 --> 00:37:13.687 position:19% line:83% align:start
