near here.

00:37:13.687 --> 00:37:15.055 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah?

00:37:16.755 --> 00:37:18.322 position:27% line:89% align:start
All cleaned up.

00:37:23.391 --> 00:37:24.057 position:30% line:89% align:start
Give it back!

00:37:25.790 --> 00:37:27.324 position:24% line:89% align:start
Give me that back!

00:37:30.358 --> 00:37:33.825 position:10% line:83% align:start
Her foreigner husband looked
like he was in a real bad mood.

00:37:34.792 --> 00:37:37.160 position:27% line:89% align:start
Did he hit her?

00:37:37.160 --> 00:37:40.060 position:10% line:83% align:start
No, she was being real nice
for a girl so young.

00:37:40.060 --> 00:37:42.428 position:7% line:89% align:start
My wife could learn something!

00:37:44.094 --> 00:37:46.029 position:10% line:89% align:start
The foreign assailant fled,

00:37:46.029 --> 00:37:48.196 position:21% line:83% align:start
taking a young woman
and a baby hostage.

00:37:48.196 --> 00:37:51.130 position:24% line:83% align:start
With the groom in
serious condition,

00:37:51.130 --> 00:37:52.930 position:19% line:83% align:start
