00:37:55.764 --> 00:37:58.865 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hey, this is serious!

00:37:58.865 --> 00:38:00.132 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm not kidding around, either!

00:38:02.667 --> 00:38:03.400 position:35% line:89% align:start
