00:38:07.501 --> 00:38:08.867 position:21% line:89% align:start
My mom's religious.

00:38:08.867 --> 00:38:09.434 position:24% line:89% align:start
All she does is...

00:38:17.403 --> 00:38:18.069 position:44% line:89% align:start
Me.

00:38:22.903 --> 00:38:23.103 position:27% line:89% align:start
Isn't she cute?

00:38:25.638 --> 00:38:28.705 position:16% line:83% align:start
