00:39:28.018 --> 00:39:30.119 position:13% line:89% align:start
I've got a family at home!

00:39:30.119 --> 00:39:31.786 position:7% line:89% align:start
Those children are my family!

00:39:33.920 --> 00:39:35.054 position:21% line:89% align:start
