00:39:37.355 --> 00:39:37.821 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'll be right back.

00:39:38.788 --> 00:39:40.488 position:27% line:89% align:start
Miyuki! Kiyoko!

00:39:42.456 --> 00:39:44.623 position:27% line:89% align:start
Miyuki! Kiyoko!

00:39:44.623 --> 00:39:45.691 position:30% line:89% align:start
Where are you?

00:39:53.458 --> 00:39:55.792 position:27% line:89% align:start
Kiyoko! Miyuki!

00:40:13.230 --> 00:40:15.129 position:7% line:89% align:start
How could you do this to me?!

00:40:17.064 --> 00:40:17.964 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's your own fault!

00:40:19.930 --> 00:40:22.831 position:27% line:83% align:start
