to anything I say!

00:40:22.831 --> 00:40:24.899 position:13% line:89% align:start
Use the scarf I made you,

00:40:24.899 --> 00:40:27.166 position:21% line:89% align:start
to mop up the blood!

00:40:27.166 --> 00:40:27.233 position:24% line:83% align:start
What have you done
with Angel?!

00:40:28.766 --> 00:40:30.434 position:30% line:83% align:start
Where is she?
Where is my Angel?

00:40:31.766 --> 00:40:32.400 position:24% line:89% align:start
She's right here.

00:40:33.435 --> 00:40:34.268 position:35% line:89% align:start
Our angel.

00:40:36.934 --> 00:40:37.935 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'm hungry.

00:40:39.035 --> 00:40:40.135 position:24% line:89% align:start
Make me some food.

00:40:41.637 --> 00:40:41.803 position:44% line:89% align:start
Why?

00:40:43.503 --> 00:40:46.171 position:5% line:89% align:start
What are you doing in my house?

00:40:46.171 --> 00:40:49.338 position:21% line:83% align:start
Miyuki, take Kiyoko.
I'll get dinner.

00:41:00.241 --> 00:41:04.442 position:27% line:89% align:start
Kiyoko! Miyuki!

00:41:09.909 --> 00:41:10.842 position:27% line:89% align:start
Geezer Grandma?!

00:41:15.711 --> 00:41:18.311 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh, I've missed you,
my little angel!

00:41:19.345 --> 00:41:20.745 position:35% line:89% align:start
