00:41:23.379 --> 00:41:25.846 position:16% line:83% align:start
I wish I was her mother.
But I'm just a queen who cares.

00:41:27.547 --> 00:41:28.080 position:38% line:89% align:start
Miyuki,

00:41:30.047 --> 00:41:31.314 position:16% line:89% align:start
I'm so glad you're safe.

00:41:41.116 --> 00:41:41.416 position:21% line:89% align:start
Where's the old man?

00:41:43.217 --> 00:41:45.084 position:27% line:83% align:start
He could be dead
for all I care!

00:41:47.918 --> 00:41:50.185 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm dying.

00:42:00.521 --> 00:42:02.887 position:21% line:89% align:start
Maybe he went home.

00:42:02.887 --> 00:42:03.154 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who cares?

00:42:05.155 --> 00:42:06.189 position:21% line:83% align:start
All he thinks about
is himself.

00:42:09.223 --> 00:42:14.057 position:10% line:83% align:start
Yeah, Miss Hana, but you're
in love with him, aren't you?

00:42:14.057 --> 00:42:18.192 position:7% line:83% align:start
