00:43:01.569 --> 00:43:02.736 position:24% line:89% align:start
Just do your job.

00:43:02.736 --> 00:43:04.403 position:44% line:89% align:start
Gin!

00:43:07.637 --> 00:43:09.437 position:35% line:89% align:start
