00:43:34.076 --> 00:43:38.277 position:24% line:89% align:start
If only tonight...

00:43:40.544 --> 00:43:43.878 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wanted to see you
before I died.

00:43:46.746 --> 00:43:49.013 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kiyoko!

00:44:05.950 --> 00:44:08.217 position:21% line:83% align:start
