My magic, or an ambulance?

00:44:10.351 --> 00:44:12.451 position:30% line:83% align:start
-An ambulance.
-Well! Aren't you rude!

00:44:14.152 --> 00:44:16.386 position:16% line:89% align:start
What are we going to do?

00:44:16.386 --> 00:44:18.720 position:24% line:83% align:start
Kiyoko can't sleep
out on the street!

00:44:18.720 --> 00:44:20.420 position:16% line:89% align:start
