00:44:25.254 --> 00:44:27.322 position:13% line:89% align:start
I guess there's no choice.

00:44:33.889 --> 00:44:35.524 position:27% line:83% align:start
I never thought
I'd be here again.

00:44:43.159 --> 00:44:46.092 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry. We're closed for
a private party tonight--

00:44:48.727 --> 00:44:49.527 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hana?!

00:44:51.193 --> 00:44:53.028 position:19% line:83% align:start
I know I have no right
to come strolling in now,

00:44:55.361 --> 00:44:58.062 position:16% line:83% align:start
but there's no one else
I can call on, "Mother"!

00:45:03.196 --> 00:45:04.363 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hana!

00:45:05.364 --> 00:45:06.864 position:38% line:89% align:start
Mother!

00:45:06.864 --> 00:45:07.897 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hana!

00:45:15.966 --> 00:45:16.466 position:35% line:89% align:start
Old man?!

00:45:20.467 --> 00:45:21.567 position:21% line:89% align:start
What happened, Gin?!

00:45:24.669 --> 00:45:26.403 position:19% line:89% align:start
