00:45:28.569 --> 00:45:30.537 position:21% line:83% align:start
I guess I'm just not
an action hero.

00:45:35.971 --> 00:45:36.971 position:27% line:83% align:start
Can't believe he
is a friend of yours.

00:45:38.871 --> 00:45:41.039 position:16% line:83% align:start
