00:45:57.842 --> 00:45:59.543 position:27% line:89% align:start
Isn't she cute?!

00:45:59.543 --> 00:46:00.476 position:16% line:89% align:start
I wish I could have one!

00:46:06.512 --> 00:46:09.413 position:21% line:89% align:start
So Ken died, did he?

00:46:11.912 --> 00:46:12.346 position:41% line:89% align:start
AIDS?

00:46:14.447 --> 00:46:17.113 position:19% line:83% align:start
He slipped on the soap
in the bathtub.

00:46:17.113 --> 00:46:19.114 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, death is always
a hair's breadth away.

00:46:21.782 --> 00:46:24.516 position:10% line:83% align:start
But if you were in trouble,
why didn't you come back?

00:46:28.216 --> 00:46:30.850 position:13% line:83% align:start
We certainly had fun here,
didn't we?

00:46:32.984 --> 00:46:34.251 position:27% line:89% align:start
In this old bar

00:46:35.851 --> 00:46:38.851 position:13% line:89% align:start
I've had so much to drink

00:46:40.286 --> 00:46:41.852 position:27% line:89% align:start
My old memories

00:46:42.986 --> 00:46:47.321 position:24% line:89% align:start
All start to blur

00:46:47.321 --> 00:46:50.021 position:38% line:89% align:start
My lover

00:46:50.021 --> 00:46:52.922 position:33% line:89% align:start
Has left me

00:46:54.723 --> 00:46:59.057 position:16% line:89% align:start
People call me notorious

00:47:00.023 --> 00:47:01.158 position:27% line:89% align:start
Aw, you're ugly!

00:47:02.358 --> 00:47:04.124 position:27% line:89% align:start
Good for nothing

00:47:04.792 --> 00:47:04.924 position:38% line:89% align:start
Get off!

00:47:05.925 --> 00:47:08.125 position:27% line:89% align:start
Good for nothing

00:47:09.826 --> 00:47:13.493 position:10% line:89% align:start
What a terrible thing to say

00:47:13.493 --> 00:47:15.461 position:27% line:89% align:start
Eat shit, Pops!

00:47:18.094 --> 00:47:21.128 position:24% line:83% align:start
"Shit" I'll take,
but "Pops" I won't!

00:47:29.164 --> 00:47:30.497 position:21% line:83% align:start
I couldn't come back
after I'd done that.

00:47:32.964 --> 00:47:36.633 position:19% line:83% align:start
A little bit of money
took care of that.

00:47:36.633 --> 00:47:38.599 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'm just happy you're all right.

00:47:42.033 --> 00:47:44.501 position:19% line:83% align:start
Stop it! You scare me
when you start crying.

00:47:47.301 --> 00:47:50.235 position:19% line:83% align:start
What about that baby?
Is the girl its mother?

00:47:50.902 --> 00:47:51.935 position:38% line:89% align:start
Well....

00:47:55.969 --> 00:47:58.870 position:7% line:89% align:start
Where is your mother, anyway?

00:48:00.371 --> 00:48:01.772 position:33% line:89% align:start
Abandoned?!

00:48:01.772 --> 00:48:04.505 position:13% line:89% align:start
Yes! I've been abandoned!

00:48:07.773 --> 00:48:09.606 position:10% line:89% align:start
Them's the breaks, I guess.

00:48:11.708 --> 00:48:12.541 position:19% line:89% align:start
I could see me in her.

00:48:15.041 --> 00:48:17.175 position:21% line:83% align:start
Born on the street,
and back there again.

00:48:19.743 --> 00:48:25.010 position:7% line:83% align:start
That's why I want to find her
a home full of love!

00:48:25.010 --> 00:48:28.911 position:10% line:89% align:start
All I ever wanted was love!

00:48:36.313 --> 00:48:36.879 position:44% line:89% align:start
Ow!

00:48:43.748 --> 00:48:45.248 position:27% line:89% align:start
What the hell?!

00:48:48.982 --> 00:48:49.982 position:24% line:83% align:start
Is there something
you wanna tell me?

00:48:51.216 --> 00:48:51.982 position:19% line:89% align:start
Where are my clothes?!

00:49:02.419 --> 00:49:03.619 position:27% line:89% align:start
Way to go, Gin!

00:49:05.919 --> 00:49:07.620 position:21% line:89% align:start
Come back any time.

00:49:09.454 --> 00:49:11.188 position:24% line:89% align:start
Thank you, Mother.

00:49:14.823 --> 00:49:16.255 position:16% line:89% align:start
My mother's white breath

00:49:16.255 --> 00:49:17.656 position:13% line:89% align:start
as she watches me set out

00:49:17.656 --> 00:49:18.489 position:24% line:89% align:start
on a long journey.

00:49:52.297 --> 00:49:52.630 position:7% line:83% align:start
DEAR HANA. A LITTLE EARLY, BUT
NEW YEAR'S MONEY. FROM MOTHER.

00:50:36.742 --> 00:50:37.641 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, man!

00:50:40.641 --> 00:50:43.008 position:5% line:83% align:start
An empty building's always nice,
but look who got here first.

00:50:47.343 --> 00:50:49.977 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'd just love to fill up
on some meat!

00:50:50.944 --> 00:50:52.378 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't you dare!

00:50:54.645 --> 00:50:56.445 position:30% line:89% align:start
Just kidding!

00:51:02.447 --> 00:51:05.447 position:24% line:83% align:start
The snow's let up.
Miyuki, will you go shopping?

00:51:05.447 --> 00:51:06.749 position:41% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:51:06.749 --> 00:51:08.315 position:24% line:89% align:start
Get me some saké.

00:51:09.515 --> 00:51:10.648 position:35% line:89% align:start
Just one.

00:51:29.420 --> 00:51:31.086 position:44% line:83% align:start
-No!
-I wish.

00:51:48.791 --> 00:51:49.424 position:24% line:89% align:start
"Honey, I'm home."

00:52:08.629 --> 00:52:13.397 position:21% line:83% align:start
You stayed in there?
You'd think you were homeless!

00:52:19.164 --> 00:52:21.265 position:10% line:83% align:start
Actually, we're looking for
these people.

00:52:23.499 --> 00:52:24.932 position:24% line:89% align:start
Sachiko Nishizawa.

00:52:25.867 --> 00:52:26.133 position:27% line:89% align:start
Do you know her?

00:52:28.634 --> 00:52:31.801 position:7% line:83% align:start
She never paid me back for her
Neighborhood Association dues.

00:52:31.801 --> 00:52:34.535 position:21% line:89% align:start
Are you a relative?

00:52:34.535 --> 00:52:37.569 position:16% line:83% align:start
No! We're acquaintances
of a relative.

00:52:39.136 --> 00:52:39.569 position:13% line:89% align:start
Her husband was no better.

00:52:42.137 --> 00:52:45.370 position:16% line:83% align:start
Gambling day and night,
and mean when he drank.

00:52:48.605 --> 00:52:51.172 position:7% line:83% align:start
Living on his wife's earnings
and borrowed money.

00:52:51.172 --> 00:52:53.506 position:21% line:89% align:start
Where are they now?

00:52:53.506 --> 00:52:55.973 position:27% line:83% align:start
I wouldn't know.
Mrs. Kurumizawa might.

00:52:57.906 --> 00:52:59.574 position:35% line:83% align:start
They left
about three months ago.

00:53:02.641 --> 00:53:07.476 position:7% line:83% align:start
The house was seized for debt.
One night they just up and went.

00:53:09.410 --> 00:53:10.610 position:16% line:83% align:start
They were a nice couple
at first,

00:53:13.310 --> 00:53:16.745 position:13% line:83% align:start
but it wasn't long before
they started fighting.

00:53:16.745 --> 00:53:19.612 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's poverty for you.

00:53:19.612 --> 00:53:23.613 position:7% line:83% align:start
All that debt didn't stop him
from lording it over her.

00:53:23.613 --> 00:53:26.280 position:10% line:83% align:start
Even the most dedicated wife
has her limits.

00:53:28.113 --> 00:53:30.014 position:10% line:89% align:start
You'd see bruises sometimes.

00:53:30.014 --> 00:53:32.114 position:27% line:89% align:start
The poor woman.

00:53:32.114 --> 00:53:34.716 position:21% line:89% align:start
Not on her, on him!

00:53:34.716 --> 00:53:34.649 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, dear!

00:53:37.482 --> 00:53:43.084 position:19% line:83% align:start
But the wife's mother
always took the husband's side.

00:53:45.117 --> 00:53:46.352 position:19% line:83% align:start
His parents built them
this house.

00:53:47.719 --> 00:53:49.886 position:21% line:89% align:start
Where do they live?

00:53:49.886 --> 00:53:51.319 position:10% line:89% align:start
Mrs. Yamanouchi might know.

00:53:54.520 --> 00:53:55.087 position:24% line:83% align:start
Her mother-in-law
was always complaining

00:53:57.053 --> 00:53:59.255 position:24% line:83% align:start
that she never did
any housework.

00:53:59.255 --> 00:54:01.522 position:16% line:83% align:start
But her son was perfect,
of course.

00:54:01.522 --> 00:54:04.856 position:35% line:83% align:start
Of course!
That's why I told her

00:54:04.856 --> 00:54:07.423 position:10% line:83% align:start
she'd never see a grandchild
with his wife working in a club.

00:54:08.956 --> 00:54:11.990 position:13% line:89% align:start
But she did get pregnant.

00:54:11.990 --> 00:54:14.324 position:10% line:89% align:start
Well, a man and a woman....

00:54:14.324 --> 00:54:16.024 position:10% line:89% align:start
They can always find time...

00:54:16.024 --> 00:54:18.592 position:19% line:89% align:start
to do what they must!

00:54:18.592 --> 00:54:21.226 position:27% line:83% align:start
SHINKOCHO 1-2-25
MAISON HAPPINESS APT. 203

00:54:23.493 --> 00:54:24.326 position:21% line:83% align:start
What if they ran out
from this new place too?

00:54:25.694 --> 00:54:26.027 position:21% line:89% align:start
What a horrible man!

00:54:28.895 --> 00:54:32.629 position:5% line:83% align:start
Poor Sachiko! Working to pay off
her husband's gambling debts!

00:54:33.529 --> 00:54:34.329 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:54:35.630 --> 00:54:38.697 position:19% line:83% align:start
But I never thought of
abandoning the kid!

00:54:40.097 --> 00:54:42.632 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Nothing.

00:54:42.632 --> 00:54:45.331 position:27% line:83% align:start
That's no reason
to just dump the kid!

00:54:46.866 --> 00:54:47.599 position:13% line:89% align:start
I've said that all along.

00:54:51.567 --> 00:54:55.268 position:24% line:83% align:start
MIYUKI: ANGEL HAS
COME HOME. DAD.

00:55:00.669 --> 00:55:02.569 position:13% line:83% align:start
Doesn't it ever get tired
of snowing?

00:55:05.670 --> 00:55:07.170 position:35% line:89% align:start
Thank you.

00:55:17.373 --> 00:55:21.507 position:21% line:83% align:start
I wonder how we look
to them.

00:55:21.507 --> 00:55:22.174 position:21% line:83% align:start
Like a bum, a queer,
a runaway and a foundling.

00:55:24.607 --> 00:55:26.708 position:13% line:83% align:start
Kiyoko is God's messenger.
We're her servants.

00:55:28.708 --> 00:55:29.709 position:27% line:89% align:start
Unpaid servants.

00:55:31.342 --> 00:55:32.975 position:10% line:89% align:start
Paying for a father's sins.

00:55:35.243 --> 00:55:38.478 position:10% line:83% align:start
Yeah, if her father had been
any good at all,

00:55:38.478 --> 00:55:39.645 position:21% line:83% align:start
we wouldn't be going
through all this.

00:55:42.712 --> 00:55:46.546 position:7% line:83% align:start
Even a good-for-nothing father
never forgets a child.

00:55:49.079 --> 00:55:50.280 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm going out.

00:55:55.281 --> 00:55:58.549 position:10% line:89% align:start
What's the matter with her?

00:55:58.549 --> 00:56:01.016 position:19% line:83% align:start
A child never forgets
its parents, either.

00:56:06.184 --> 00:56:08.585 position:21% line:89% align:start
I never stop wanting

00:56:10.485 --> 00:56:13.052 position:7% line:89% align:start
to see my daughter, just once.

00:56:13.052 --> 00:56:14.619 position:27% line:89% align:start
So she's alive?

00:56:15.586 --> 00:56:16.952 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:56:16.952 --> 00:56:17.554 position:30% line:89% align:start
And your wife?

00:56:19.420 --> 00:56:20.986 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm sure she's remarried,

00:56:22.188 --> 00:56:23.987 position:21% line:89% align:start
and living happily.

00:56:29.289 --> 00:56:30.056 position:38% line:89% align:start
"Hello.

00:56:31.123 --> 00:56:32.156 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's me, Miyuki."

00:56:33.590 --> 00:56:34.256 position:19% line:89% align:start
Why did you split up?

00:56:36.090 --> 00:56:37.324 position:16% line:83% align:start
-Drinking and gambling.
-What?!

00:56:38.991 --> 00:56:39.692 position:30% line:89% align:start
Just like....

00:56:41.459 --> 00:56:42.725 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'm a louse.

00:56:45.793 --> 00:56:49.093 position:10% line:83% align:start
But I've always wanted to do
something for her as a father,

00:56:50.260 --> 00:56:50.727 position:21% line:89% align:start
even just a little.

00:56:53.495 --> 00:56:54.728 position:21% line:83% align:start
When I was gambling
this would have been nothing.

00:56:57.463 --> 00:57:00.530 position:10% line:83% align:start
Now I've had to sweat blood
just to save 30,000 yen.

00:57:00.530 --> 00:57:01.597 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's great, Gin!

00:57:03.030 --> 00:57:03.730 position:16% line:89% align:start
We can stuff ourselves!

00:57:04.765 --> 00:57:05.631 position:35% line:89% align:start
Stuff you!

00:57:15.934 --> 00:57:16.667 position:27% line:89% align:start
Ishida speaking.

00:57:26.169 --> 00:57:28.670 position:21% line:89% align:start
Miyuki? Is that you?

00:57:31.604 --> 00:57:32.337 position:24% line:89% align:start
Are you all right?

00:57:38.738 --> 00:57:40.172 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry!

00:57:40.172 --> 00:57:41.506 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry!

00:57:42.539 --> 00:57:43.973 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry!

00:57:47.106 --> 00:57:49.308 position:35% line:83% align:start
Excuse me,
but if you wouldn't mind....

00:57:49.308 --> 00:57:49.508 position:21% line:89% align:start
"Get out," you mean?

00:57:51.608 --> 00:57:55.242 position:27% line:83% align:start
Other customers
might like to sit down.

00:57:55.242 --> 00:57:56.543 position:10% line:89% align:start
There's hardly anyone here!

00:57:56.543 --> 00:57:57.410 position:27% line:89% align:start
You guys stink!

00:57:59.510 --> 00:58:01.377 position:30% line:83% align:start
What are you?
Homeless or something?

00:58:03.845 --> 00:58:06.645 position:13% line:83% align:start
Does trash have kids too?
Just like real people?

00:58:08.078 --> 00:58:09.580 position:16% line:89% align:start
Who are you looking at?

00:58:12.213 --> 00:58:13.079 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hold it, you!

00:58:14.380 --> 00:58:16.414 position:38% line:89% align:start
Sir! No!

00:58:16.414 --> 00:58:17.614 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hold it, I said, you low-life!

00:58:28.784 --> 00:58:29.983 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's New Year's Sale time
at The Food Store!

00:58:32.885 --> 00:58:39.085 position:7% line:83% align:start
Come to The Food Store for all
your special New Year's needs!

00:58:39.085 --> 00:58:41.687 position:21% line:83% align:start
See in the New Year
with your family!

00:58:41.687 --> 00:58:42.620 position:13% line:89% align:start
Call an ambulance, quick.

00:58:43.821 --> 00:58:44.688 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right!

00:58:49.322 --> 00:58:52.690 position:10% line:83% align:start
I knew it! Kiyoko really is
the messenger of God!

00:58:55.756 --> 00:58:55.656 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

00:58:57.057 --> 00:58:57.157 position:35% line:89% align:start
Miss Hana!

00:58:57.791 --> 00:58:59.424 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

00:58:59.424 --> 00:59:00.057 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hana!

00:59:17.461 --> 00:59:17.661 position:24% line:83% align:start
Following a recent
gang shooting incident,

00:59:20.729 --> 00:59:24.563 position:7% line:83% align:start
police are seeking a fugitive,
thought to be of Latin descent.

00:59:26.230 --> 00:59:27.164 position:5% line:89% align:start
Mitsuo Hiruta, shot three times,

00:59:29.464 --> 00:59:31.097 position:16% line:83% align:start
in protecting the leader
of his syndicate,

00:59:33.732 --> 00:59:37.566 position:16% line:83% align:start
will be questioned after
he recovers from his wounds.

00:59:39.533 --> 00:59:41.667 position:27% line:83% align:start
Isn't she cute!
When was she born?

00:59:43.100 --> 00:59:45.235 position:19% line:89% align:start
Not long ago, I guess.

00:59:46.301 --> 00:59:47.869 position:24% line:89% align:start
So the mother....

00:59:47.869 --> 00:59:49.069 position:38% line:89% align:start
I'm not.

00:59:50.035 --> 00:59:51.369 position:27% line:89% align:start
What's her name?

00:59:51.369 --> 00:59:53.237 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kiyoko.

00:59:53.237 --> 00:59:56.070 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's my name too.
What a coincidence.

00:59:59.371 --> 01:00:02.539 position:13% line:89% align:start
Your friend is very weak.

01:00:02.539 --> 01:00:04.038 position:13% line:83% align:start
Make sure she gets plenty
of rest and proper nutrition.

01:00:04.739 --> 01:00:05.405 position:38% line:89% align:start
Doctor!

01:00:07.373 --> 01:00:09.707 position:24% line:83% align:start
Believe it or not,
we're homeless.

01:00:09.707 --> 01:00:11.241 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm just a doctor.

01:00:14.040 --> 01:00:18.242 position:10% line:83% align:start
Rest and nutrition don't fit
with our lifestyle, you realize.

01:00:19.910 --> 01:00:23.611 position:13% line:89% align:start
I can try to cure disease.

01:00:23.611 --> 01:00:24.611 position:19% line:83% align:start
Lifestyle is something
you have to fix.

01:00:26.277 --> 01:00:28.712 position:5% line:89% align:start
All anyone can do is their best.

01:00:31.613 --> 01:00:33.045 position:35% line:89% align:start
Take care.

01:00:37.447 --> 01:00:40.915 position:24% line:83% align:start
The bill for today
is 29,830 yen.

01:00:40.915 --> 01:00:44.047 position:5% line:83% align:start
Bring your health insurance card
and you'll get a refund.

01:00:45.616 --> 01:00:47.249 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry, Gin!

01:00:49.483 --> 01:00:52.049 position:16% line:83% align:start
Stop crying! You'll get
the bills all wet.

01:00:53.217 --> 01:00:54.684 position:24% line:89% align:start
That's 30,000 yen.

01:01:11.388 --> 01:01:12.221 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kiyoko?!

01:01:17.589 --> 01:01:18.256 position:44% line:89% align:start
Dad?

01:01:41.862 --> 01:01:43.328 position:16% line:89% align:start
So you took up nursing.

01:01:45.029 --> 01:01:46.796 position:41% line:89% align:start
I see.

01:01:49.898 --> 01:01:52.397 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm glad you're well.

01:01:52.397 --> 01:01:57.164 position:13% line:83% align:start
Oh, yeah, I'm just great.
How's your mother?

01:01:57.164 --> 01:01:58.165 position:41% line:89% align:start
Fine.

01:01:59.666 --> 01:02:01.165 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah? That's good.

01:02:02.400 --> 01:02:04.834 position:16% line:89% align:start
What are you doing now?

01:02:04.834 --> 01:02:10.067 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm in recycling. I had to
drop something off here.

01:02:14.702 --> 01:02:15.737 position:24% line:89% align:start
You must hate me.

01:02:18.370 --> 01:02:20.337 position:21% line:83% align:start
I was never any kind
of a father to you.

01:02:22.971 --> 01:02:27.605 position:7% line:83% align:start
But that 30,000 yen was money
I'd saved up for you.

01:02:29.773 --> 01:02:30.640 position:16% line:89% align:start
You may not believe it.

01:02:34.841 --> 01:02:37.241 position:10% line:89% align:start
I always wanted to see you.

01:02:39.775 --> 01:02:41.743 position:24% line:83% align:start
When I was little,
Mom and I searched for you.

01:02:44.042 --> 01:02:45.310 position:27% line:83% align:start
We even checked
unidentified corpses.

01:02:47.810 --> 01:02:51.044 position:19% line:83% align:start
After you disappeared,
Mom ran the store herself.

01:02:52.211 --> 01:02:54.579 position:35% line:89% align:start
The store?

01:02:54.579 --> 01:02:57.245 position:7% line:83% align:start
It was hard for a woman to run
a bicycle shop alone.

01:02:59.513 --> 01:03:01.113 position:10% line:83% align:start
That's not quite the same as
a bicycle racer.

01:03:02.447 --> 01:03:06.314 position:13% line:89% align:start
The man you owed money to

01:03:06.314 --> 01:03:08.582 position:21% line:83% align:start
was shot and wounded
the other day, you know.

01:03:08.582 --> 01:03:09.382 position:35% line:89% align:start
He lived?!

01:03:10.882 --> 01:03:13.449 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's a relief.

01:03:13.449 --> 01:03:14.716 position:13% line:89% align:start
I thought you'd say that.

01:03:18.350 --> 01:03:22.385 position:10% line:89% align:start
I ran up the debts, not him.

01:03:25.452 --> 01:03:28.654 position:13% line:83% align:start
Thank that doctor for me.
He seems like a nice guy.

01:03:30.220 --> 01:03:32.086 position:21% line:89% align:start
I'm getting married.

01:03:34.288 --> 01:03:36.087 position:27% line:89% align:start
Oh? That's good.

01:03:36.087 --> 01:03:38.188 position:38% line:89% align:start
To him.

01:03:38.188 --> 01:03:40.756 position:21% line:83% align:start
Great! But isn't he
about my age?

01:03:43.456 --> 01:03:45.591 position:24% line:83% align:start
He's been married.
His daughter got sick and died,

01:03:47.157 --> 01:03:48.791 position:13% line:89% align:start
and his wife followed her.

01:03:54.893 --> 01:03:56.693 position:13% line:89% align:start
That man makes me so mad!

01:03:56.693 --> 01:03:57.393 position:24% line:89% align:start
Aren't you moved?

01:03:59.460 --> 01:04:01.794 position:24% line:83% align:start
Here's the address
and phone number.

01:04:01.794 --> 01:04:02.060 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yours?

01:04:03.295 --> 01:04:06.295 position:19% line:89% align:start
The old house is gone.

01:04:06.295 --> 01:04:07.496 position:19% line:83% align:start
Even if you can't now,
call me sometime.

01:04:09.129 --> 01:04:11.195 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kiyoko!

01:04:14.096 --> 01:04:17.831 position:30% line:83% align:start
I've had about
all I can stand!

01:04:17.831 --> 01:04:19.097 position:35% line:89% align:start
Miss Hana?

01:04:19.097 --> 01:04:21.198 position:10% line:89% align:start
Telling us you were a racer!

01:04:22.866 --> 01:04:24.767 position:13% line:89% align:start
I was always at the track.

01:04:24.767 --> 01:04:24.733 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yeah, betting!

01:04:27.166 --> 01:04:31.334 position:10% line:83% align:start
And your debts snowballed so
you couldn't face your family,

01:04:31.334 --> 01:04:32.801 position:21% line:83% align:start
and you ran and hid
in a cardboard box!

01:04:32.801 --> 01:04:35.002 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yes, damn it!

01:04:35.002 --> 01:04:35.468 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's what your father is!

01:04:38.536 --> 01:04:42.337 position:7% line:83% align:start
He can't bet, he's spineless,
his feet stink and he's a drunk!

01:04:42.337 --> 01:04:46.271 position:19% line:83% align:start
He kills off his wife
and daughter to buy sympathy!

01:04:46.271 --> 01:04:49.204 position:13% line:83% align:start
He said you had died from
an incurable disease.

01:04:49.204 --> 01:04:52.539 position:16% line:83% align:start
With a father like that,
you have my sympathy!

01:04:54.105 --> 01:04:56.373 position:13% line:89% align:start
Is this how you repay me?!

01:04:57.273 --> 01:04:58.140 position:33% line:89% align:start
Repay you?!

01:04:59.308 --> 01:04:59.441 position:21% line:89% align:start
Am I hearing right?

01:05:02.107 --> 01:05:04.242 position:10% line:83% align:start
If we're talking about debt,
I'm waiting for my change!

01:05:04.242 --> 01:05:04.475 position:27% line:83% align:start
Debt's a concept
you don't even understand!

01:05:07.043 --> 01:05:10.577 position:10% line:83% align:start
You understand how to troll
through garbage cans!

01:05:10.577 --> 01:05:13.744 position:19% line:83% align:start
And how to get in debt
and how to make babies.

01:05:13.744 --> 01:05:17.412 position:13% line:83% align:start
Though you're not too good
at raising them, are you?

01:05:17.412 --> 01:05:20.546 position:30% line:83% align:start
And your debts
you shove off on your wife.

01:05:20.546 --> 01:05:21.613 position:21% line:83% align:start
Always running away,
never doing anything right!

01:05:23.980 --> 01:05:25.147 position:30% line:83% align:start
Running away's
the only racing you ever did!

01:05:26.380 --> 01:05:28.781 position:19% line:89% align:start
Miyuki! We're leaving!

01:05:31.982 --> 01:05:32.782 position:35% line:89% align:start
Miss Hana?

01:05:39.051 --> 01:05:40.350 position:13% line:89% align:start
Someone's feeling better.

01:05:42.585 --> 01:05:44.785 position:13% line:83% align:start
Should you have said that
in front of her?

01:05:48.619 --> 01:05:50.853 position:19% line:83% align:start
If she's his daughter,
she'll forgive him.

01:05:54.520 --> 01:05:57.955 position:13% line:89% align:start
Being able to speak freely

01:05:57.955 --> 01:06:00.121 position:13% line:89% align:start
is the lifeblood of love.

01:06:01.689 --> 01:06:02.522 position:27% line:89% align:start
Maybe I'm nïve.

01:06:06.156 --> 01:06:09.090 position:10% line:89% align:start
So you're in love with him?

01:06:09.090 --> 01:06:11.857 position:27% line:83% align:start
Don't be silly.
I'm the "Blue Devil".

01:06:11.857 --> 01:06:12.291 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?

01:06:13.458 --> 01:06:15.491 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's a story I love.

01:06:17.026 --> 01:06:20.026 position:13% line:89% align:start
There was a Red Devil who

01:06:20.026 --> 01:06:20.526 position:33% line:83% align:start
wanted to be
friends with people.

01:06:23.427 --> 01:06:28.261 position:13% line:83% align:start
But since he was a devil,
no one would go near him.

01:06:28.261 --> 01:06:30.495 position:10% line:83% align:start
So his friend the Blue Devil
made a plan.

01:06:32.529 --> 01:06:35.763 position:27% line:83% align:start
He'd wreak havoc
among the people,

01:06:35.763 --> 01:06:37.330 position:24% line:83% align:start
and the Red Devil
would save them.

01:06:43.565 --> 01:06:45.131 position:27% line:83% align:start
WHEN YOU TRY TO
ACHIEVE SOMETHING...

01:06:45.131 --> 01:06:45.865 position:10% line:89% align:start
SOMEONE'S BOUND TO GET HURT.

01:06:48.232 --> 01:06:49.433 position:24% line:83% align:start
YOU ALWAYS HAVE TO
SACRIFICE SOMETHING.

01:06:50.800 --> 01:06:51.500 position:27% line:89% align:start
The plan worked.

01:06:53.500 --> 01:06:56.401 position:24% line:83% align:start
But the Blue Devil
had to go away

01:06:56.401 --> 01:06:57.468 position:21% line:83% align:start
so they'd never know
it was a trick.

01:07:00.936 --> 01:07:03.336 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's a sad story.

01:07:03.336 --> 01:07:05.637 position:13% line:83% align:start
But that means you leave.
Where will you go?

01:07:08.671 --> 01:07:11.438 position:10% line:83% align:start
It's best for everyone when
they're with their real family.

01:07:11.438 --> 01:07:11.738 position:5% line:89% align:start
Soon we'll find Kiyoko's mother.

01:07:14.305 --> 01:07:17.373 position:30% line:83% align:start
And then what?
You don't have a real family!

01:07:28.076 --> 01:07:32.043 position:5% line:89% align:start
RARE 'LINE OF ONES' WINS LOTTERY

01:07:32.043 --> 01:07:34.444 position:5% line:83% align:start
Numbers have been drawn for the
annual New Year's Jumbo Lottery.

01:07:37.510 --> 01:07:39.345 position:5% line:83% align:start
Top prize in the 200-million-yen
lottery is a very rare number.

01:07:40.945 --> 01:07:43.646 position:13% line:89% align:start
Group 11, number 111, 111,

01:07:45.112 --> 01:07:46.713 position:16% line:89% align:start
is worth 50 million yen.

01:07:48.880 --> 01:07:49.180 position:24% line:83% align:start
A different group
pays 100,000 yen.

01:07:51.414 --> 01:07:53.581 position:35% line:83% align:start
To repeat,
the winning prize number is....

01:07:56.016 --> 01:07:56.248 position:30% line:89% align:start
This just in.

01:07:58.782 --> 01:08:02.483 position:7% line:83% align:start
Police have released a sketch
of an infant taken

01:08:02.483 --> 01:08:05.250 position:24% line:83% align:start
from a hospital in
Tokyo's Shinagawa Ward.

01:08:08.919 --> 01:08:13.620 position:10% line:83% align:start
We've come all the way here,
but we don't have her address!

01:08:13.620 --> 01:08:16.020 position:19% line:83% align:start
The old man's got it!
Let's go back.

01:08:16.020 --> 01:08:17.654 position:21% line:89% align:start
Where are you going?

01:08:20.454 --> 01:08:23.521 position:33% line:83% align:start
-The police!
-What? You hated that idea!

01:08:25.055 --> 01:08:25.889 position:16% line:89% align:start
I was just ego-tripping.

01:08:28.189 --> 01:08:31.890 position:16% line:83% align:start
Now I want to apologize
to her parents.

01:08:31.890 --> 01:08:33.857 position:5% line:83% align:start
They might not be able to sleep
waiting for news about her.

01:08:36.291 --> 01:08:39.525 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's what we said
from the very start!

01:08:39.525 --> 01:08:42.225 position:10% line:89% align:start
They might be even about to

01:08:42.225 --> 01:08:44.493 position:30% line:83% align:start
commit suicide
because of the regret.

01:08:44.493 --> 01:08:47.494 position:21% line:83% align:start
I've done something
that can't be taken back!

01:08:47.494 --> 01:08:50.361 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'll throw myself in this river.

01:08:50.361 --> 01:08:52.462 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'll step neatly
out of my shoes,

01:08:52.462 --> 01:08:54.929 position:19% line:83% align:start
stand on the handrail,
and be at peace.

01:08:54.929 --> 01:08:55.795 position:24% line:83% align:start
But then I'll see
a baby's face on the water.

01:08:58.329 --> 01:09:01.597 position:27% line:83% align:start
No! While I see
this child's face, I cannot die!

01:09:02.597 --> 01:09:04.098 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hey, you!

01:09:04.098 --> 01:09:05.298 position:44% line:89% align:start
No!

01:09:08.198 --> 01:09:09.299 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're too young for this!

01:09:09.299 --> 01:09:10.766 position:21% line:89% align:start
Please! Let me die!

01:09:18.901 --> 01:09:20.234 position:44% line:89% align:start
You!

01:09:21.334 --> 01:09:22.268 position:24% line:89% align:start
Sachiko Nishizawa.

01:09:27.336 --> 01:09:27.770 position:10% line:89% align:start
What were you thinking of?!

01:09:29.470 --> 01:09:32.204 position:5% line:89% align:start
Weren't you going to apologize?

01:09:32.204 --> 01:09:35.872 position:7% line:83% align:start
If we hadn't found this child,
she would've frozen to death!

01:09:35.872 --> 01:09:37.772 position:30% line:89% align:start
It wasn't me!

01:09:37.772 --> 01:09:39.840 position:16% line:83% align:start
My husband took her away
when I wasn't there!

01:09:41.873 --> 01:09:43.774 position:16% line:89% align:start
I've looked and looked!

01:09:51.808 --> 01:09:52.442 position:30% line:89% align:start
Is that true?

01:09:56.577 --> 01:10:00.645 position:24% line:83% align:start
All I've suffered
on account of that man!

01:10:12.246 --> 01:10:14.748 position:35% line:89% align:start
"Hi, Mom!"

01:10:23.816 --> 01:10:25.616 position:10% line:83% align:start
God really loves this child,
you know.

01:10:27.817 --> 01:10:29.384 position:19% line:83% align:start
I want you to give her
lots of love too.

01:10:31.451 --> 01:10:34.019 position:27% line:83% align:start
Do right by her,
or you'll pay for it.

01:10:34.019 --> 01:10:35.986 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm so sorry!

01:10:35.986 --> 01:10:36.719 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry!

01:10:47.187 --> 01:10:48.489 position:27% line:89% align:start
Mrs. Nishizawa!

01:11:35.600 --> 01:11:35.833 position:10% line:89% align:start
What are you doing in here?!

01:11:37.100 --> 01:11:38.566 position:13% line:89% align:start
Get out of here! Get out!

01:11:39.934 --> 01:11:40.601 position:21% line:89% align:start
Wait! I'm no thief.

01:11:42.035 --> 01:11:44.301 position:19% line:89% align:start
You're lying! Get out!

01:11:44.301 --> 01:11:44.835 position:24% line:89% align:start
Where's the baby?!

01:11:49.703 --> 01:11:52.503 position:13% line:83% align:start
Did an old hag and a girl
come to give it back?

01:11:52.503 --> 01:11:54.203 position:10% line:89% align:start
What are you talking about?!

01:11:54.203 --> 01:11:55.637 position:19% line:89% align:start
You abandoned a baby!

01:11:58.271 --> 01:11:59.838 position:27% line:89% align:start
I can prove it.

01:12:01.005 --> 01:12:03.739 position:30% line:89% align:start
Are you a cop?

01:12:03.739 --> 01:12:07.407 position:21% line:83% align:start
Huh? I'm just a bum
who was passing by.

01:12:09.273 --> 01:12:11.608 position:13% line:89% align:start
Are you right in the head?

01:12:11.608 --> 01:12:12.241 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm damn near crazy
from all this!

01:12:13.708 --> 01:12:16.876 position:7% line:89% align:start
Why is the baby you abandoned

01:12:16.876 --> 01:12:19.309 position:21% line:83% align:start
on the news as being
"taken away"?

01:12:19.309 --> 01:12:20.543 position:10% line:89% align:start
They'll call us kidnappers!

01:12:22.510 --> 01:12:25.644 position:30% line:83% align:start
It wasn't me.
That's not my kid.

01:12:28.578 --> 01:12:28.945 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?

01:12:31.479 --> 01:12:33.946 position:16% line:89% align:start
There, there! Don't cry!

01:12:33.946 --> 01:12:34.513 position:35% line:89% align:start
Take care.

01:12:35.646 --> 01:12:37.480 position:27% line:89% align:start
Raise her right.

01:12:37.480 --> 01:12:38.914 position:19% line:89% align:start
See you again someday.

01:12:41.348 --> 01:12:43.448 position:19% line:89% align:start
Never leave her again.

01:13:06.854 --> 01:13:08.688 position:19% line:89% align:start
On the year's last day

01:13:08.688 --> 01:13:10.254 position:30% line:83% align:start
when all of a
life's accounts

01:13:10.254 --> 01:13:11.321 position:19% line:89% align:start
have been settled up.

01:13:24.925 --> 01:13:29.793 position:16% line:83% align:start
Sachiko stole that baby
out of the hospital.

01:13:29.793 --> 01:13:32.627 position:27% line:83% align:start
She stole a baby
and then abandoned it?!

01:13:34.061 --> 01:13:34.694 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's a person's life!

01:13:36.094 --> 01:13:39.261 position:16% line:89% align:start
She lied to me about it!

01:13:39.261 --> 01:13:40.662 position:24% line:83% align:start
And now it's gone
way out of control.

01:13:42.796 --> 01:13:44.395 position:19% line:83% align:start
I don't want anything
to do with it!

01:13:44.395 --> 01:13:45.963 position:10% line:89% align:start
Take the kid to the police!

01:13:46.863 --> 01:13:47.763 position:41% line:89% align:start
What?!

01:13:49.831 --> 01:13:53.065 position:30% line:83% align:start
Don't act like
you're not part of this!

01:13:53.065 --> 01:13:54.265 position:5% line:83% align:start
You don't want to get involved?
You're her husband!

01:13:56.832 --> 01:13:59.433 position:10% line:83% align:start
That's all over! I'm getting
my life back together.

01:14:00.100 --> 01:14:01.633 position:41% line:89% align:start
Look!

01:14:01.633 --> 01:14:04.001 position:24% line:83% align:start
I won 100,000 yen
in the lottery.

01:14:04.001 --> 01:14:04.867 position:24% line:89% align:start
My luck's turned!

01:14:08.702 --> 01:14:09.868 position:10% line:89% align:start
I know a guy just like you.

01:14:11.936 --> 01:14:13.736 position:30% line:83% align:start
He threw away
his life and his family.

01:14:15.336 --> 01:14:16.370 position:13% line:89% align:start
No. He threw himself away.

01:14:17.336 --> 01:14:18.837 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm no loser!

01:14:24.539 --> 01:14:25.872 position:7% line:89% align:start
These were in your wife's bag.

01:14:29.273 --> 01:14:30.640 position:30% line:83% align:start
Any idea where
she might have gone?

01:14:32.941 --> 01:14:34.741 position:19% line:83% align:start
She said she was going
to be with her baby.

01:14:36.441 --> 01:14:38.542 position:7% line:89% align:start
She was going to kill herself!

01:14:41.010 --> 01:14:43.077 position:13% line:89% align:start
There's no time to waste!

01:14:43.077 --> 01:14:46.877 position:19% line:83% align:start
No! She was just going
to go look for the kid.

01:14:46.877 --> 01:14:48.310 position:27% line:83% align:start
She's desperate.
That only means one thing!

01:14:50.578 --> 01:14:51.611 position:19% line:89% align:start
But where do I look?!

01:15:08.049 --> 01:15:09.183 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hana!

01:15:09.183 --> 01:15:10.248 position:38% line:89% align:start
Miyuki!

01:15:12.184 --> 01:15:13.249 position:38% line:89% align:start
Kiyoko!

01:15:20.552 --> 01:15:23.019 position:27% line:83% align:start
God must be busy
at this time of year.

01:15:23.019 --> 01:15:24.619 position:7% line:89% align:start
Better once a year than never.

01:15:25.920 --> 01:15:26.252 position:38% line:89% align:start
Old man?

01:15:37.023 --> 01:15:40.456 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're too late. You just missed
a very moving finale.

01:15:40.456 --> 01:15:41.857 position:24% line:89% align:start
What's the matter?

01:15:46.125 --> 01:15:46.658 position:35% line:89% align:start
"Kiyoko"!

01:15:50.425 --> 01:15:50.926 position:35% line:89% align:start
"Stomach"?

01:15:53.759 --> 01:15:53.926 position:35% line:89% align:start
"Mother"!

01:15:55.326 --> 01:15:57.060 position:21% line:89% align:start
Now that's settled,

01:15:57.060 --> 01:15:57.393 position:10% line:89% align:start
what the hell do you mean?!

01:15:59.427 --> 01:16:02.327 position:24% line:83% align:start
Fake! The mother!
Sachiko's a fake!

01:16:04.962 --> 01:16:05.662 position:38% line:89% align:start
Pardon?

01:16:11.897 --> 01:16:13.397 position:21% line:89% align:start
Why won't you drink?

01:16:15.798 --> 01:16:18.598 position:21% line:83% align:start
A baby has to drink
from its mother's breast.

01:16:20.632 --> 01:16:23.766 position:21% line:83% align:start
We'll never be close
if you don't!

01:16:30.835 --> 01:16:31.835 position:21% line:89% align:start
Sorry. Wrong people.

01:16:34.936 --> 01:16:35.969 position:24% line:89% align:start
She can't be far!

01:16:37.403 --> 01:16:39.636 position:19% line:89% align:start
But where do we look?

01:16:39.636 --> 01:16:41.470 position:7% line:89% align:start
We can't just give her up now!

01:16:54.941 --> 01:16:55.941 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's Kiyoko!

01:17:03.909 --> 01:17:05.676 position:19% line:89% align:start
Should you be running?

01:17:05.676 --> 01:17:07.510 position:5% line:89% align:start
If I don't run now, when will I?

01:17:08.376 --> 01:17:08.844 position:35% line:89% align:start
This way!

01:17:24.214 --> 01:17:26.181 position:19% line:83% align:start
Returning stolen goods
to a thief!

01:17:26.181 --> 01:17:27.981 position:13% line:89% align:start
How could we be so dumb?!

01:17:27.981 --> 01:17:29.582 position:13% line:89% align:start
Who said "family suicide"?

01:17:29.582 --> 01:17:30.682 position:38% line:89% align:start
You did!

01:17:37.483 --> 01:17:38.617 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Which way?
-Left.

01:17:38.617 --> 01:17:39.617 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Okay, right!
-Why?

01:17:41.051 --> 01:17:42.485 position:16% line:89% align:start
You're a lousy gambler!

01:17:42.485 --> 01:17:44.518 position:21% line:89% align:start
You got that right.

01:17:44.518 --> 01:17:45.952 position:30% line:89% align:start
Somebody help!

01:17:59.889 --> 01:18:00.856 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

01:18:01.756 --> 01:18:02.956 position:41% line:89% align:start
Wait!

01:18:02.956 --> 01:18:04.823 position:30% line:89% align:start
Thief! Thief!

01:18:04.823 --> 01:18:05.757 position:30% line:89% align:start
What's wrong?

01:18:05.757 --> 01:18:08.724 position:10% line:89% align:start
A woman just stole my truck!

01:18:09.858 --> 01:18:10.357 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hey! Thief!

01:18:11.290 --> 01:18:12.625 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yes! That woman!

01:18:14.025 --> 01:18:16.325 position:21% line:89% align:start
She's a baby thief!

01:18:31.829 --> 01:18:33.997 position:21% line:83% align:start
Be quiet, will you?
Please! Be a good baby!

01:18:43.032 --> 01:18:44.599 position:16% line:89% align:start
Stop! Give Kiyoko back!

01:18:49.800 --> 01:18:51.734 position:27% line:89% align:start
Give me a break!

01:18:51.734 --> 01:18:53.034 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm forever in your debt!

01:18:58.735 --> 01:18:59.401 position:44% line:89% align:start
Gin!

01:19:01.636 --> 01:19:03.302 position:21% line:89% align:start
That woman's crazy!

01:19:04.270 --> 01:19:04.470 position:33% line:89% align:start
Get closer!

01:19:05.138 --> 01:19:06.270 position:38% line:89% align:start
I can't!

01:19:06.270 --> 01:19:08.972 position:16% line:89% align:start
You have to, for Kiyoko!

01:19:08.972 --> 01:19:10.671 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Who's Kiyoko?!
-Step on it like a man!

01:19:10.671 --> 01:19:11.404 position:41% line:89% align:start
Okay!

01:19:16.874 --> 01:19:18.840 position:24% line:89% align:start
Please! Be quiet!

01:19:23.142 --> 01:19:24.008 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Gin!
-Old man?!

01:19:27.642 --> 01:19:29.642 position:38% line:89% align:start
Old man!

01:19:29.642 --> 01:19:31.810 position:27% line:83% align:start
Go for it, Gin!
No action star can touch you!

01:19:32.810 --> 01:19:34.377 position:35% line:89% align:start
Pass her!

01:19:34.377 --> 01:19:34.477 position:35% line:89% align:start
We'll die!

01:19:35.377 --> 01:19:35.511 position:33% line:89% align:start
Step on it!

01:19:36.211 --> 01:19:37.511 position:41% line:89% align:start
Okay!

01:19:39.812 --> 01:19:40.645 position:33% line:89% align:start
Stop crying!

01:19:42.913 --> 01:19:44.746 position:27% line:83% align:start
Don't be afraid.
I'll never leave you again.

01:19:46.013 --> 01:19:46.479 position:24% line:89% align:start
You want to die?!

01:19:55.949 --> 01:19:57.549 position:44% line:89% align:start
Gin!

01:20:09.919 --> 01:20:10.986 position:44% line:89% align:start
Gin!

01:20:13.887 --> 01:20:14.553 position:41% line:89% align:start
There!

01:20:17.221 --> 01:20:18.554 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Are you okay?!
-Where's Kiyoko?

01:20:18.554 --> 01:20:19.621 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Faster!
-Okay!

01:20:39.826 --> 01:20:39.726 position:35% line:89% align:start
Which way?

01:21:27.637 --> 01:21:27.837 position:24% line:89% align:start
We're at the scene

01:21:30.404 --> 01:21:34.939 position:13% line:83% align:start
where a truck has crashed
into a building in Shinagawa.

01:21:34.939 --> 01:21:37.639 position:13% line:83% align:start
Now a woman holding a baby
has appeared on the roof.

01:21:39.107 --> 01:21:40.706 position:16% line:89% align:start
Witnesses say the woman

01:21:40.706 --> 01:21:44.241 position:5% line:89% align:start
is connected with the incident,

01:21:44.241 --> 01:21:45.641 position:7% line:89% align:start
as she was driving the truck.

01:21:52.743 --> 01:21:54.676 position:16% line:83% align:start
Now there's someone else
on the roof!

01:21:59.911 --> 01:22:00.878 position:35% line:89% align:start
Stay away!

01:22:00.878 --> 01:22:02.611 position:44% line:89% align:start
No!

01:22:10.413 --> 01:22:11.680 position:21% line:83% align:start
Tell me why you took
that baby.

01:22:12.480 --> 01:22:12.547 position:35% line:89% align:start
I didn't!

01:22:13.648 --> 01:22:17.015 position:24% line:89% align:start
This baby is mine!

01:22:17.015 --> 01:22:19.482 position:7% line:83% align:start
You're lying! Its real parents
are worried sick about it!

01:22:19.482 --> 01:22:22.082 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's not true!

01:22:22.082 --> 01:22:24.683 position:7% line:83% align:start
You of all people should know
what it's like to lose a child!

01:22:37.519 --> 01:22:41.520 position:16% line:83% align:start
She's dead. My baby died
before she was even born!

01:22:50.123 --> 01:22:53.224 position:7% line:83% align:start
All the other babies looked so
healthy there in the ward.

01:22:53.224 --> 01:22:56.456 position:27% line:89% align:start
I wanted to die.

01:22:56.456 --> 01:22:58.958 position:24% line:83% align:start
But then this baby
smiled at me.

01:22:58.958 --> 01:23:01.826 position:16% line:89% align:start
I decided she was mine.

01:23:01.826 --> 01:23:05.993 position:5% line:83% align:start
I thought as long as I had her,
everything would be fine.

01:23:05.993 --> 01:23:09.093 position:5% line:83% align:start
My husband would mend his ways,
and we'd be a real family.

01:23:09.093 --> 01:23:09.594 position:27% line:89% align:start
That's bullshit!

01:23:11.794 --> 01:23:14.495 position:30% line:83% align:start
Build a family
by ruining a baby's life?

01:23:14.495 --> 01:23:15.062 position:16% line:83% align:start
If you're going to die,
do it alone!

01:23:17.395 --> 01:23:19.629 position:24% line:83% align:start
A life is a life.
It's only born once.

01:23:19.629 --> 01:23:21.096 position:21% line:89% align:start
You, me, or Kiyoko.

01:23:27.199 --> 01:23:28.631 position:21% line:89% align:start
Give her back, okay?

01:23:36.433 --> 01:23:37.800 position:21% line:89% align:start
I want to be reborn.

01:23:39.134 --> 01:23:40.835 position:38% line:89% align:start
Sachiko!

01:23:43.302 --> 01:23:46.535 position:21% line:83% align:start
Sachiko, don't die!
Come back to me!

01:23:46.535 --> 01:23:48.636 position:33% line:83% align:start
I was wrong!
Please, don't kill yourself!

01:23:50.570 --> 01:23:52.070 position:24% line:83% align:start
We'll start again!
We'll be reborn!

01:23:52.938 --> 01:23:55.238 position:38% line:89% align:start
Sachiko!

01:23:55.238 --> 01:23:57.371 position:5% line:89% align:start
I'll go first and wait for you.

01:24:01.940 --> 01:24:02.706 position:38% line:89% align:start
Sachiko!

01:24:05.707 --> 01:24:07.540 position:21% line:89% align:start
Please! Let me die!

01:24:07.540 --> 01:24:09.674 position:21% line:83% align:start
Kiyoko wants to see
her mom and dad!

01:24:16.210 --> 01:24:16.909 position:24% line:89% align:start
I want to go home.

01:24:20.877 --> 01:24:22.710 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm sorry!

01:24:30.812 --> 01:24:31.046 position:38% line:89% align:start
Take her

01:24:32.580 --> 01:24:34.613 position:13% line:89% align:start
to her mother and father.

01:24:44.249 --> 01:24:44.749 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, no.

01:24:46.116 --> 01:24:46.983 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hana!

01:24:49.184 --> 01:24:49.884 position:35% line:89% align:start
I'm okay!

01:24:51.084 --> 01:24:51.884 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm still alive!

01:25:33.694 --> 01:25:37.761 position:16% line:83% align:start
Inspector, I don't know
how to thank you.

01:25:37.761 --> 01:25:40.529 position:24% line:83% align:start
We're not the ones
you should thank.

01:25:43.996 --> 01:25:48.630 position:10% line:83% align:start
Man, that was a good sleep!
Get me a cigarette, Miyuki.

01:25:48.630 --> 01:25:50.731 position:30% line:83% align:start
-In my jacket.
-Yeah, yeah.

01:25:50.731 --> 01:25:53.565 position:13% line:89% align:start
That was some New Year's!

01:25:55.066 --> 01:25:55.599 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's "No Smoking" here.

01:25:57.032 --> 01:26:00.133 position:16% line:89% align:start
Lighten up! I'm a hero!

01:26:00.133 --> 01:26:01.700 position:30% line:89% align:start
You mean "we"!

01:26:05.901 --> 01:26:08.768 position:27% line:83% align:start
I guess we won't
have to listen to

01:26:08.768 --> 01:26:11.436 position:7% line:89% align:start
Kiyoko's damn crying anymore.

01:26:11.436 --> 01:26:13.369 position:10% line:89% align:start
She's not "Kiyoko" anymore.

01:26:13.369 --> 01:26:15.470 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm not pleased.

01:26:16.537 --> 01:26:18.537 position:27% line:89% align:start
What can we do?

01:26:18.537 --> 01:26:19.738 position:27% line:89% align:start
Not about that.

01:26:21.172 --> 01:26:22.638 position:19% line:89% align:start
This is a men's ward!

01:26:26.139 --> 01:26:27.505 position:16% line:89% align:start
Perhaps we're intruding.

01:26:27.505 --> 01:26:28.974 position:30% line:89% align:start
No, it's just,

01:26:30.540 --> 01:26:33.041 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm told they're homeless.

01:26:33.041 --> 01:26:34.808 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who cares?

01:26:34.808 --> 01:26:36.809 position:21% line:83% align:start
We'd like them to be
her godfathers.

01:26:39.009 --> 01:26:39.642 position:38% line:89% align:start
Come in.

01:26:41.244 --> 01:26:41.476 position:35% line:89% align:start
Excuse us.

01:26:43.810 --> 01:26:45.944 position:24% line:83% align:start
The baby's parents
would like to thank you--

01:26:52.079 --> 01:26:52.979 position:38% line:89% align:start
Dad....

